data.description: Welcome to this beautiful, like new home on almost half an acre in Saraland. This charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath residence boasts a perfect blend of comfort and style. Once inside you will see LVP flooring throughout the home. The kitchen features beautiful granite countertops, perfect for preparing meals and entertaining guest. The open floor plan is ample for entertaining guest and creating a warm atmosphere. New Roof in 2021 along with new windows, plumbing, electrical and an automated fence.
